    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Right, the equity thing is a big part of it. But from an environmental standpoint, most of the data suggests it's one of the most effective ways to hit emissions targets. Do you think it's actually viable to keep delaying these kinds of policies if we want to meet climate goals?",
